none/30a8a220e9a2253866bdf7e8c8c8b2e7/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_27_2__0.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"黃又南多年後再入圍角逐金像獎。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d6fc74edbcc8158cb44b9a2fbfa80e0/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_27_3__0.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"金像獎「最佳女配角」候選人衛詩雅造型照曝光。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/464a87eb64b50abf41540a8fda4bba4a/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_29_3__0.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"衛詩雅去年憑《破．地獄》首奪「最佳女主角」。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7bee7afd0ff26513c764937b609a44c/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_30_1__0.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"衛詩雅在《再見UFO》中飾演與奇幻事件糾纏的都巿女子。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b961f2b45c92ea7447376ac66a99842/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_30_0.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"金像獎「最佳女配角」惠英紅的造型照。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/740643986ef7179734a6022626d2480f/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_28_2_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"滕麗名笑容燦爛。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7fdce476acca40d7d0ff56151d3befd/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_29_2_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"入圍金像獎「最佳女配角」滕麗名的造型照。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8a9d45eff39bb4862400c504925c20b/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_29.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"金像獎「最佳女配角」候選人鄧濤造型照曝光。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/16db56c88ea1042da4b7ce162b6dacb5/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_30_3_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"金像獎「最佳女配角」候選人鮑起靜造型照曝光。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/595152e623bc7789bec22ccaf44e7969/2026-03/WhatsApp_Image_2026-03-30_at_15_20_31_2_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李佳芯憑《金童》中的「方靈」一角首度角逐金像獎。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f466fa4aeb256f8a77db46ef5e621bbb/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-02_at_4_12_15_PM_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"鄧濤憑《女孩不平凡》雙料入圍今屆「最佳女配角」及「最佳新演員」。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a0bab9a9f223f249a196673aea2cd050/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-02_at_4_12_13_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"李哲坤憑《捕風追影》中的「仔仔」一角躋身今屆「最佳新演員」五強。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/84ad634c5ae4afb1566018f3118eb942/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-02_at_4_12_16_PM_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"蘇子茵在《給愛麗絲》飾演逃離家暴的少女「愛麗絲」。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef55cb668a3cffce7d2fe884b10ba452/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-02_at_4_12_14_PM_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"年僅14歲的周衹月、現為香港足球代表隊U16成員。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/18dd0d5f39eecc14ca44a9c897f313ed/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-02_at_4_12_16_PM_3_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"周衹月首次參演電影即以《逆轉上半場》中的「曾芷瑩」一角入圍金像獎「最佳新演員」。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cad7592939fd92ff0ec0cf0160d2d64e/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-02_at_4_12_17_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<p>在期待今屆盛事之餘，不妨一同重溫去年第43屆金像獎紅地氈的璀璨星光。當時由沈殷怡與強尼擔任主持，一眾巨星盛裝出席，包括夫妻檔現身的梁朝偉與劉嘉玲、擔任「最佳衣着獎」評審的王丹妮、型格登場的Marf邱彥筒，以及妙語如珠的劉青雲等。當時大熱電影如《破·地獄》及《九龍城寨之圍城》的團隊亦是紅地氈焦點。</p>\n<img alt=\"《焚城》團隊\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/866242ed6b38f2647f3de1008d0e5e96/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-27_at_6_21_42_PM_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"鄧麗欣（左）透視Deep V好性感。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/3ff67985e590d032a9c6589960beceba/2024-04/Image_150_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"林明禎（左）貼身裙騷身材。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/7bfadaf83555375b36c43d3c615aac9c/2024-04/Image_157_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"Ian陳卓賢\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/fb537ad443dc320498e0c424c4907c78/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-27_at_5_26_07_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"馮德倫、Angelababy楊穎\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/d1135de204b11e9b446c12e19f445d38/2024-04/Image_173_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"林熙蕾\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/33b7bb5ab34fa8cb8734fc517bb85e3d/2024-04/Image_116_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"洪金寶與高麗虹一同到場。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/2805f43ec055f6b3f6a1c6b368dadf7f/2024-04/Image_169_.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"是枝裕和\" src=\"https://image